title: Google\Cloud\AppEngine\V1\ZipInfo
name: ZipInfo
description:
The zip file information for a zip deployment.

Generated from protobuf message google.appengine.v1.ZipInfo

Extends Google\Protobuf\Internal\Message

params.name: data
params.description: Optional. Data for populating the Message object.

params.name: data.source_url
params.description: URL of the zip file to deploy from. Must be a URL to a resource in Google Cloud Storage in the form 'http(s)://storage.googleapis.com/\<bucket>/\<object>'.

params.name: data.files_count
params.description: An estimate of the number of files in a zip for a zip deployment. If set, must be greater than or equal to the actual number of files. Used for optimizing performance; if not provided, deployment may be slow.
